'''強淋溶土'''（通用名稱{{lang|en|Acrisols}}）是一種由[[聯合國糧食及農業組織|聯合國糧食及農業組織]]劃分的[[土壤|土壤]] 。它是一種含豐富[[黏土|黏土]]的土壤，與濕潤的熱帶氣候相關，例如在[[巴西|巴西]] ，而且往往支撐[[森林|森林]]地區<ref>{{cite book|title=Chemistry of Variable Charge Soils|author=T. R. Yu|year=1997|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=0-19-509745-9|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=70yqVLEn95QC&pg=PA36&ots=iDgjL3QwLT&dq=Acrisol&ie=ISO-8859-1&output=html&sig=jHEUUPtOyK4Z8Dvj5-lm9UZO61U|page=36|access-date=2009-07-04|archive-date=2012-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111111549/http://books.google.com/books?id=70yqVLEn95QC&pg=PA36&ots=iDgjL3QwLT&dq=Acrisol&ie=ISO-8859-1&output=html&sig=jHEUUPtOyK4Z8Dvj5-lm9UZO61U|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它是[[世界土壤參考基準|世界土壤參考基準]]30個主要群體的之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fao.org/docrep/W8594E/w8594e00.htm |title=World reference base for soil resources |accessdate=2009-07-04 |archive-date=2018-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216015002/http://www.fao.org/docrep/w8594e/w8594e00.HTM |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
[[File:Acrisol.png|right]]
強淋溶土的類別是：
*ACf Ferric Acrisols
*ACg Gleyic Acrisols
*ACh Haplic Acrisols
*ACp Plinthic Acrisols
*ACu Humic Acrisols

